---
title: Mexican Bean & Veggie Chilli with Cheddar Cheese & Homemade Tortilla Chips
description: Making your own veggie chilli? Easy. Making your own crispy tortilla chips to go with it? Even easier! We promise.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-bean-veggie-chilli-bde50a99.jpg
